creator: Kayan Bible
descriptionHtml:
The Kayan Bible app contains the books of the Bible that have been translated so far by the Kayan Bible Translation Team: Luke, Acts, Romans, Ephesians, Colossians, and Psalms 90-150. (Mark, 1 & 2 Thessalonians have been translated but need to be improved for consistent spelling before publishing.)

We welcome your comments, questions, and advice. Please email us or call us. We will be happy to hear from you.

Don't forget to check out the Ephesians + Colossians audio app and the Psalm Songs app!

You can use this app offline once installed. No internet or data connection required.
